a rather negative look at motherhood i 've read lots of pregnancy books , and this book came recommended as an `` honest '' view . it may be honest , but very negative ! i realize that motherhood is n't usually the fairytale many of us hope it will be , but this book just dwelled on the negatives : sometimes you ca n't figure out breastfeeding , sometimes you worry that your husband might leave you , sometimes the baby wo n't stop crying ... . hopefully there are more books out there that are more evenly balanced with `` real life '' stories . i recommend that you keep looking